🔷 Security Requirements
Identity & Access

Create IAM role for DataSync with:

s3:PutObject

s3:AbortMultipartUpload

s3:GetBucketLocation

s3:ListBucket

kms:Encrypt (if SSE-KMS used)

Enforce:

No wildcard resource permissions

Explicit bucket-level ARN restrictions

Encryption

In Transit:

TLS 1.2 minimum

Private connectivity if possible (VPC endpoint)

At Rest:

S3 bucket must enforce:

SSE-KMS encryption

Bucket policy requiring encryption header

Network Security

If source is EC2:

Deploy DataSync agent in same VPC

Use private subnets

Use S3 Gateway VPC Endpoint

Block public S3 access

If on-prem:

Use IP allowlisting

Restrict outbound traffic

Use VPN or Direct Connect (if available)

🔷 S3 Configuration

Create bucket:

prod-was-log-archive
Enable:

Versioning

Default encryption (SSE-KMS)

Block public access (all enabled)

Access logging (optional)

Lifecycle policies:

Age	Transition
30 days	S3 Glacier Instant Retrieval
180 days	S3 Glacier Deep Archive
365 days	Expire
🔷 DataSync Configuration
Agent

Deploy DataSync agent (EC2 or VMware)

Use minimal instance type (m5.large or as required)

Harden OS:

Disable SSH password auth

Patch to latest AMI

Restrict security group inbound

Locations

Create:

Source location:

NFS or SMB (or EC2 file system path)

Destination location:

S3 bucket path:

s3://prod-was-log-archive/{hostname}/yyyy/mm/dd/
Task Configuration

Schedule: Daily at 1 AM

Options:

Verify mode: ONLY_FILES_TRANSFERRED

Overwrite mode: NEVER

Preserve deleted files: OFF

Transfer mode: CHANGED files only

Bandwidth limit: configurable (if required)

Enable:

CloudWatch logs

Task reports

🔷 Monitoring & Alerting

Configure:

CloudWatch metrics alarms for:

Task failure

Bytes transferred below threshold

Agent offline

SNS notification topic for:

Failure alerts

🔷 Cost Optimization Controls

Use compression at source (gzip before transfer)

Transfer only rotated logs

Avoid CloudWatch ingestion (costly)

Use lifecycle to move to Glacier tiers

Avoid cross-region transfer unless required

🔷 Observability & Governance

Enable:

CloudTrail logging

S3 server access logging (optional)

Tag all resources:

Environment: PROD

Owner: PlatformTeam

CostCenter: IT-Infra

